dialNew :: Rectangle -> Maybe String -> IO (Ref Dial)
dialNew rectangle l'=
    let (x_pos, y_pos, width, height) = fromRectangle rectangle
    in case l' of
        Nothing -> dialNew' x_pos y_pos width height >>=
                             toRef
        Just l -> dialNewWithLabel' x_pos y_pos width height l >>=
                               toRef
